{"tid":87841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林日曦:  唔使話鍾意食薯片鍾意到咁樣樣下嘛","createTime":"2017-01-20T07:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T12:06:27.000Z","uid":22054,"like":53,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30b142cc0524f2038d4845372eca8b190be4efd8","tid":87841,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:04:32.000Z","msg":"大家受過鷹派特首五年高壓統治之後，意屬鴿派薯片都係人之常情，明嘅，咁你搵枝來福槍隊住我個雲精迫我四揀一我可能或者都會被迫揀薯片。不過，都唔使話鍾意食薯片鍾意到咁樣樣下嘛大家..<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示佢尋日再次表明會為23條立法。其實在現存制度下最終能夠被選上嘅人，毫無疑問都會將中共利益置先於香港人利益。你哋明㗎啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/linrixi/posts/1231461070279229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flinrixi%2Fposts%2F1231461070279229&d=ohugl7sx8BWB9kVPH%2BgyFJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=6b78d80d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/linrixi/posts/1231461070279229</a>"},{"pid":"8dadf4d1af55f8d7a68d279a73a9ce43000966f3","tid":87841,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/150925_25227383b1c9ba4ce041c9d56585e08f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F150925_25227383b1c9ba4ce041c9d56585e08f.jpg&h=58f16f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870d7cf0c3e73b1ed6afb9363ef9d63127a409b6","tid":87841,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/150925_25227383b1c9ba4ce041c9d56585e08f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F150925_25227383b1c9ba4ce041c9d56585e08f.jpg&h=58f16f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />